Document: ShaderMaterial
Path: godot/classes/class_shadermaterial.rst
Summary: ShaderMaterial class methods for accessing and modifying shader parameters.

Method: get_shader_parameter(param: StringName) → Variant
Returns the current value of the specified shader parameter. This method is const, indicating it does not modify the object's state.

Method: set_shader_parameter(param: StringName, value: Variant)
Sets the value of the specified shader parameter. This method allows dynamic modification of shader properties at runtime, enabling effects like animated materials or parameter-driven visual changes. The parameter name must match exactly with the shader's defined uniform variables.
---CHUNK---
